mcgill.xtext.turn.utils

Class YangNameUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • mcgill.xtext.turn.utils.YangNameUtils

  • public abstract class YangNameUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for getting the YANG name from EObject instances and EClasses.

    For instance YangVersion will return with turn-version.
